&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own day-to-day accounting operations, including processing and posting all accounts payable and accounts receivable transactions&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Review and approve AP/AR entries for accuracy and completeness prior to management review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare and post month-end close journal entries, including accruals and partner reconciliations&lt;/li&gt;
