&lt;li&gt;Experience in a private company environment is required or have transitioned from public to private accounting&amp;nbsp; for at least one year&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ownership Mindset: Proactive and self-driven with a strong sense of initiative, consistently taking responsibility, and exceeds expectations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;High attention to detail, has capacity to get stuff done, and stay organized&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
