&lt;p&gt;In this role, you will analyze how Nift’s&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;auction systems, pricing dynamics, and experimentation frameworks&lt;/strong&gt; impact brand performance, consumer engagement, and company revenue. You will translate complex system behavior into clear actionable insights. You will partner with &lt;strong&gt;Sales, Product, and Data Science&lt;/strong&gt; to guide product decisions and explain marketplace performance to brand partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a high-impact role for someone who enjoys solving &lt;strong&gt;complex business problems with data&lt;/strong&gt;, working across teams, and turning analytical insights into decisions that influence revenue.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Our Mission:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Nift’s mission is to reshape how people discover and try new brands by introducing them to new products and services through thoughtful &quot;thank-you&quot; gifts. Our customer-first approach ensures businesses acquire new customers efficiently while making customers feel valued and rewarded.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are a data-driven, cash-flow-positive company that has experienced &lt;strong&gt;731% growth over the last three years. &lt;/strong&gt;As we scale, data and analytics are central to how we make decisions, improve performance, and explain value to our partners.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Backed by investors who supported Fitbit, Warby Parker, and Twitter, we are poised for exponential growth and ready to demonstrate impact on a global scale. Read more about our growth&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.businesswire.com/news/home/20251119582928/en/Nift-Ranked-Number-120-Fastest-Growing-Company-in-North-America-on-the-2025-Deloitte-Technology-Fast-500&quot;&gt; here&lt;/a&gt;.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze the economics and performance of Nift’s marketplace and auction systems&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify drivers of brand performance, pricing efficiency, and customer acquisition outcomes&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Evaluate experiments, model calibration changes, and feature launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with our revenue team to provide insights, explain marketplace behavior and performance trends, pricing dynamics to brands&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform root-cause analysis, investigate unexpected revenue shifts, performance changes, and anomalies&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Define and track key revenue, marketplace health, and growth metrics&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate complex analyses into clear narratives and recommendations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product and Data Science to improve marketplace performance and optimization strategies by measuring A/B tests, model calibration changes, and feature launches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure data accuracy, consistency, and trust across all analyses and deliverables&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;5–7+ years of experience in &lt;strong&gt;data analytics, growth analytics, or revenue analytics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong proficiency in SQL and comfort working with large, complex datasets&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Working knowledge of experimentation analysis (A/B tests) and performance measurement&lt;/li&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Nift is disrupting performance marketing, delivering millions of new customers to brands every month. As we enter our next phase of hypergrowth, we’re looking for a &lt;strong&gt;Senior Talent Acquisition Specialist&lt;/strong&gt; to join our People team and help build the foundation of our future success.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the VP of People, this is a high-visibility, high-impact role supporting the entire organization. You’ll own full-cycle recruiting for priority roles and partner closely with the leadership team and hiring managers across the company. We believe every hire directly impacts our business, exceptional hiring is core to our future success.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;As a Senior Talent Acquisition Specialist, you’ll execute full-cycle recruitment (sourcing, screening, interviewing, offers). You’ll build and move high-quality candidate pipelines, serve as a strong ambassador for Nift in the market, and deliver a best-in-class candidate and hiring manager experience.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
