&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What you will do:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own full-cycle recruiting for assigned roles&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner closely with hiring managers and other stakeholders to understand&amp;nbsp; requirements, responsibilities, and desired outcomes for each assigned position&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
