&lt;li&gt;Proactively use outbound techniques, tools, and resources to identify, engage, and recruit targeted candidates&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Use multiple channels and creative approaches to build strong candidate pipelines&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Relentlessly prioritize quality over volume without compromising velocity&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Deliver a professional, responsive and exceptional candidate experience&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Keep candidates informed and engaged throughout the process&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Represent the company credibly in the market&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prepare hiring managers for interviews and feedback&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive timely decision-making and clear hiring signals&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flag issues early when scope, process or expectations are off&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate pipeline data in the ATS (Greenhouse)&lt;/li&gt;
